The Process

How It Works

1

Get a Quote

Text "QUOTE" to (781) 632-8313 or email TJselfiestation@gmail.com with your event details.

2

Book Your Date

We confirm availability, finalize your package, and lock in your event date.

3

We Set Up

We arrive early, set up the full booth, backdrop, and props — stress-free for you.

4

Enjoy & Share

Guests take unlimited photos, get instant prints, and receive their digital gallery.
